{"tid":1776254,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)霧地異煞 黑魔塔 閃靈 安眠醫生","createTime":"2019-12-09T11:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T14:19:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e57736adbdb7fffe470ca023b9c4607ccb5e3d1","tid":1776254,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=20fb95fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=b6c4d863\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OKRU 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=dbffc3fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a1/The_Mist_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa1%2FThe_Mist_poster.jpg&h=28c6da5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/The_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg&h=d22264de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.radiozero.cl/static/2016/06/the-shining.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.radiozero.cl%2Fstatic%2F2016%2F06%2Fthe-shining.jpg&h=017c0bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/travelerwithmovie.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/unnamed-file.jpg?fit=680%2C957&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Ftravelerwithmovie.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Funnamed-file.jpg%3Ffit%3D680%252C957%26ssl%3D1&h=111b4187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一場暴風雨，鄰居諾頓律師的樹木倒塌，打壞電影海報畫家大衛德雷頓（湯瑪斯&middot;傑恩飾）的畫室，大衛和他的妻子看見不尋常的霧開始從山間蔓延，全鎮亦斷電。為重整風暴摧殘後的家園，大衛和5歲的兒子比利（納桑&middot;蓋博飾），與鄰居諾頓（安德魯&middot;布瑞格飾）去當地的超市採賣物品。到了店內，越來越多的警車在街上奔馳，引起顧客注意，最終空襲警報響起，一名老人丹米勒（傑佛瑞&middot;狄蒙飾）滿面鮮血，狼狽的跑進超市，警告大家有迎面而來的濃霧中有異物，非常駭人<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述在文明崩壞世界中，羅蘭&middot;德斯欽是名主要以雙左輪手槍為武器的僅存槍客，他希望能在宇宙的中樞「黑塔」找到阻止自己世界滅亡的方法<br />\n<br />\n3.傑克&middot;托倫斯(Jack Torrance)是一名作家，為了擺脫工作上的失意，接受了一份在冬天維護科羅拉多州一家奢華的山間飯店的工作。他年幼的兒子擁有通靈能力，能夠看到過去和未來的東西，如棲息在飯店的鬼魂。到飯店安頓好後不久，這家人就被暴風雪困住了，傑克逐漸受到一個超自然的存在的影響；他陷入瘋狂並企圖謀殺他的妻子和兒子...<br />\n<br />\n4.《閃靈》裡的小孩丹尼在經歷了35年前的酒店事件後，經成為一個四十歲的大男人，在過去的十年裡，丹尼重蹈父親的覆轍，成為了一個酗酒者，丹尼最終定居在一個小鎮上，並且在一家養老院找到工作，在那裡他殘餘的閃靈力量為垂死之人提供了至關重要的最終安慰...<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=c52ad8f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=7313a24b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe1752bee351b31682ec45c2ff162ea5d63a4cc","tid":1776254,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"點解Shining幅圖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66e687ee9b0948884bf31bce12c2104978506b6","tid":1776254,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fe1752bee351b31682ec45c2ff162ea5d63a4cc","tid":1776254,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"點解Shining幅圖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全無問題"},{"pid":"93fc6e60313f76e608caaa59ade1022c301e0ebd","tid":1776254,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06636226e5f57df4ff1758bc34b36524111d8a6","tid":1776254,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4e6aded408149c19af7a901804f55babdc4128","tid":1776254,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.